descriptions.en: It resembles a certain Pokémon introduced in a paranormal magazine, described as the offspring of a Hydreigon that fell in love with a robot.
descriptions.es: It resembles a certain Pokémon introduced in a paranormal magazine, described as the offspring of a Hydreigon that fell in love with a robot.
descriptions.ca: Sembla un determinat Pokémon que es va presentar en una revista sobre fenòmens paranormals, descrit com la cria d'un Hydreigon que s'havia enamorat d'un robot.
